c: 2
v: 266
t: "Koo aliwo mwinywe wenya okhuba nende omukunda kwetsitende, nende emizabibu, okuburangamwo emialo, ne anyolangamwo ebiamo bietsimbia tsiosi. Mana obukofu bumulile naye nali nende Abana abatiti, mana omukunda oko kukhupwe nende imbumbuyeka yomulilo mana nikuyia, Endio nilwa Nyasaye abechesilinjia ebimanyisio khomunyoole okhupara"